longBusinessSummary: General Finance and Development, Inc., through its subsidiaries, provides capital and business development services to small and mid-size companies. The company offers capital to qualified companies by equity and/or strategic loan agreements; and manages investment fund and pursues merger/acquisitions and joint venture projects. It also provides business development services, such as business planning, organization, and management development services. In addition, the company offers turnkey art procurement and consulting services; and asset management programs. Further, it develops computerized heart screen technology with programs to prevent heart disease and promote health and fitness; and provides capital for financing purposes. General Finance and Development, Inc. was founded in 2003 and is based in Minneapolis, Minnesota.
